article.description: — Johni Broome registered 19 points and eight rebounds as Morehead State topped Austin Peay 66-55 on Saturday.
article.headline: Broome lifts Morehead St. over Austin Peay 66-55
article.linkText: Broome lifts Morehead St. over Austin Peay 66-55
article.story: CLARKSVILLE, Tenn. -- — Johni Broome registered 19 points and eight rebounds as Morehead State topped Austin Peay 66-55 on Saturday. Ta'lon Cooper had seven rebounds for Morehead State (10-5, 2-0 Ohio Valley Conference), which earned its fourth straight victory. Elijah Hutchins-Everett had 15 points for the Governors (4-9, 0-3), whose losing streak stretched to six games.
